sqlQueries.sqlQuery:
select
	personName Name,
	personId,
	count(*) Apperances
from
	(
	select
		*
	from
		(
		select
			personName,
			personId,
			value1 result
		from
			Results
		where
			eventId = '333'
			and value1 > 0
	union all
		select
			personName,
			personId,
			value2 result
		from
			Results
		where
			eventId = '333'
			and value2 > 0
	union all
		select
			personName,
			personId,
			value3 result
		from
			Results
		where
			eventId = '333'
			and value3 > 0
	union all
		select
			personName,
			personId,
			value4 result
		from
			Results
		where
			eventId = '333'
			and value4 > 0
	union all
		select
			personName,
			personId,
			value5 result
		from
			Results
		where
			eventId = '333'
			and value5 > 0) r
	order by
		result
	limit 100) final
group by
	personName,
	personId
order by
	Apperances desc

select
	personName Name,
	personId,
	count(*) Apperances
from
	(
	select
		personName,
		personId,
		average
	from
		Results r
	where
		eventId = '333'
		and average > 0
	order by
		average
	limit 100) r
group by
	personName,
	personId
order by
	Apperances desc
